"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Hello, Kokoro-chan! Have plans for the day?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Yes, I do! Hello, Happy World! is taking a trip to the museum!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Wow, you are? Are they having a special exhibition or something?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Yep! They're showing dinosaurs! I can't wait to see what kind of dinos I'll get to meet! I'm so excited!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"That does sound fun... Wait, speaking of, didn't you girls end up in the news for finding the fossil of one?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Oh, you know about that? Yeah, we did, and because of that, we wanted to learn more about them.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"I-I see... The real question is how you were able to find one in the first place.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"The spot we needed to go to was drawn on a treasure map!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"What? A treasure map? Uhh, what do you mean?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Here, I'll explain everything!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"An... adventure...? All of this has strayed a little too far from reality to click with me, but I can tell you're doing some amazing stuff on your days off at the very least...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"They're really fun you know! Have you two ever been on one?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"jaan01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"I... don't think so...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Neither of you have? Then you guys need to get to it!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"When you go on an adventure, you realize just how many wonderful things there are in this world! Things you didn't even know about!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"You'll come across sights and creatures you've never seen before. And you might even find some yummy food!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Wonderful things I didn't know about, huh...? Yeah, that sure would leave an impression.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"I have to say, just hearing you talk about this kind of thing makes me wanna go somewhere I've never been before too.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"I know it would be lots of fun! Hunting for new things is just so exciting!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"jaan01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"I wanna find more and more places where I can go on adventures!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Is there any place in particular you'd like to go?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Well, I've never been to the South Pole! I'd love to go there! Doesn't having a snowball fight with the penguins sound like a great time?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"And I've never been to the bottom of the ocean! I'm not sure what kind of world awaits down there, but whatever it is, I'm sure it's lovely!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Oh, and then-","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Fufu, sounds like you've got quite the list.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Of course I do. There are just so many places I know nothing about. There's lots of fun to be had with the other members of Hello, Happy World!, and I wanna have it!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev48-me3-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectR